The requirement for the CT-scan protocol for the proper assessment of pancreatic tumors resectability. The study aims the determination of the CT-scan protocol for the proper assessment of pancreatic tumors respectability. The goal of the CT-scan is a proper visualization of the tumor spread onto the surgically important vessels of the hepatopancreatobiliary zone and remote metastases verification. The diagnostic algorithm of the pancreatic cancer is based on the analysis of the variety of cases and diagnostic means.